archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.name: S&C Vulnerability Management Development
archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation:
This is a draft of the S&C Vulnerability Management Development work package definition, based on work done in the S&C Architecture Domain team to define the project. To be aligned with the CISO team work. Note: Jan Drasal was given responsability for the Vunerability Management work by Susanne Lindstrom (Head of S&C) in Q2 of 2022.
All designs will adhere/address following: - Required People and the processes - Security policies and best practises - Information and data in the system - Dependencies to other services - Connect Sovereign in-country operations requirements - Standard IT Service Management - Capacity management - Availability, resilience and disaster recovery - Risk management - End user & operator trainings
